A chieftain of the All Progressives Congress (APC) and presidential hopeful, Bola Tinubu has stated that his chances of winning the ticket of the party are high. According to NAN, Tinubu stated this on Sunday during his visit to Taraba to meet with APC delegates in the state. “My chances of winning the ticket are incredibly high and I am very confident. I am sure I can and I will win it,” he said. Also Read: BREAKING: Coalition Picks N100m APC Nomination Forms For AfDB President, Adesina Speaking on the possibility of a consensus arrangement, Tinubu said he would prefer a democratic process on the selection of the choice of who would become the APC flagbearer in the 2023 presidential election. “I want democracy; I am voting for democracy — one man, one vote,” he said.